==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
{{etymon|grc|id=to scratch|:inh|grk-pro:*grə́pʰō<id:to scratch>}}
From {{inh|grc|grk-pro|*grə́pʰō}}, from {{der|grc|ine-pro|*gerbʰ-}}.<ref>{{R:grc:Beekes|285|γράφω}}</ref> Cognates include {{cog|ang|ċeorfan}} ({{cog|en|carve}}), {{cog|cu|жрѣбъ}}.

===Pronunciation===
{{grc-IPA|γρά˘φω}}

===Verb===
{{grc-verb|γρᾰ́φω}}

# {{lb|grc|Homeric}} to [[scratch]], [[cut]] into
#* {{Q|grc|Homer|Iliad|17|599|quote='''γράψεν''' δέ οἱ ὀστέον ἄχρις / αἰχμὴ Πουλυδάμαντος {{...}}|trans=and the spearpoint of Polydamas '''scratched''' him close to the bone {{...}}}}
# to [[draw]], [[sketch]], [[paint]]
# to [[write]]
# to write down, propose a law
#* {{Q|grc|Xen.|Hell.|1|7|34|quote=ταῦτ’ εἰπὼν Εὐρυπτόλεμος '''ἔγραψε''' γνώμην κατὰ τὸ Καννωνοῦ ψήφισμα κρίνεσθαι τοὺς ἄνδρας δίχα ἕκαστον.|trans=After saying this, Euryptolemus '''proposed''' a resolution that the men be tried under the decree of Cannonus, each one separately.}}
# {{lb|grc|middle}}
## {{lb|grc|indirect reflexive}} write down for oneself, note down
##* {{Q|grc|Plato|Theaetetus|143|a|quote=Τερψίων &nbsp; ἀτὰρ τίνες ἦσαν οἱ λόγοι; ἔχοις ἂν διηγήσασθαι;<br>Εὐκλείδης &nbsp; οὐ μὰ τὸν Δία, {{...}} ἀλλ’ '''ἐγραψάμην''' μὲν τότ’ εὐθὺς οἴκαδ’ ἐλθὼν ὑπομνήματα {{...}} .|trans=Terpsion: But what was the talk? Can you repeat it?<br>Eucleides: No, by Zeus, but I '''wrote myself''' notes as soon as I came home.}}
## to [[indict]], [[prosecute]]
##* {{Q|grc|Demosthenes|18|13|quote=δεῖ {{...}} ταῖς ἐκ τῶν νόμων τιμωρίαις παρ’ αὐτὰ τἀδικήματα χρῆσθαι, {{...}} εἰ δὲ γράφοντα παράνομα, παρανόμων '''γραφόμενον'''|trans=he must make use of the legal punishments for these crimes: {{...}} if [I] proposed illegal measures, '''to indict''' [me] for breaking the law}}
##: {{ux|grc|οἱ γραψάμενοι|the prosecutors}}
# {{lb|grc|perfect passive}} be written down, be in written form
#* {{Q|grc|Plato|Theaetetus|143|a|quote=Εὐκλείδης &nbsp; {{...}} ὥστε μοι σχεδόν τι πᾶς ὁ λόγος '''γέγραπται'''.|trans=Eucleides: &nbsp; {{...}} So I have pretty much the whole conversation written down.}}

